%20India%20can%20take%20this%20matter%20up%20with%20the%20United%20Nations...%20so%20a%20peacekeeping%20force%20can%20be%20sent%20to%20Bangladesh%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20thundered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20she%20was%20not%20seeking%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20internal%20affairs%20of%20another%20country%2C%20but%20pointed%20out%20that%20when%20Bangladeshi%20fishermen%20had%20mistakenly%20entered%20Indian%20waters%2C%20or%20when%20a%20Bangladeshi%20trawler%20had%20capsized%2C%20her%20government%20had%20%26quot%3Brescued%20them%20and%20treated%20them%20(well)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733124240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Flvhjk7jg_mamata-banerjee_650x400_17_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-wants-un-peacekeeping-force-in-bangladesh-says-pm-modi-must-intervene-7152915%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20called%20for%20a%20United%20Nations%20peacekeeping%20force%20be%20deployed%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20demanded%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20personal%20intervention%20to%20secure%20the%20safety%20of%20religious%20minorities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-wants-un-peacekeeping-force-in-bangladesh-says-pm-modi-must-intervene-7152915%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Don't%20cause%20inconvenience'%3A%20SC%20asks%20farmer%20leader%20to%20ensure%20peaceful%20protests%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733124198000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115891826%2Cimgsize-1664801.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fdont-cause-inconvenience-supreme-court-asks-farmer-leader-dallewal-to-ensure-peaceful-protests%2Farticleshow%2F115891729.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20advised%20Punjab%20farmer%20leader%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%20to%20ensure%20protests%20do%20not%20obstruct%20highways.%20Dallewal%20had%20been%20taken%20to%20a%20Ludhiana%20hospital%20but%20has%20since%20rejoined%20the%20protest%2C%20continuing%20his%20fast-unto-death%20for%20legal%20MSP%20backing.%20He%20claimed%20his%20hospitalization%20was%20forced%20and%20akin%20to%20detention%2C%20with%20no%20medical%20investigations%20conducted.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20Grant%20Bail%2C%20Next%20Day...%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%20Surprised%20In%20Senthil%20Balaji%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExpressing%20surprise%20at%20DMK%20leader%20Senthil%20Balaji's%20reinstatement%20as%20Tamil%20Nadu%20minister%20shortly%20after%20he%20was%20granted%20bail%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20said%20anyone%20will%20get%20the%20impression%20that%20the%20witnesses%20against%20the%20politician%20will%20be%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20petition%20that%20sought%20recall%20of%20the%20judgment%20granting%20bail%20to%20the%20DMK%20leader.%20The%20bench%20refused%20to%20interfere%20on%20merits%20because%20the%20Senthil%20Balaji%20bail%20order%20has%20benefited%20others%20seeking%20relief.%20The%20court%20said%20it%20would%20limit%20the%20petition's%20scope%20to%20whether%20witnesses%20against%20Mr%20Balaji%20were%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20grant%20bail%20and%20the%20next%20day%20you%20go%20and%20become%20Minister%2C%20anybody%20will%20be%20bound%20under%20the%20impression%20that%20now%20with%20your%20position%20as%20a%20senior%20Cabinet%20Minister%20witnesses%20will%20be%20under%20pressure.%20What%20is%20this%20going%20on%3F%26quot%3B%20Justice%20AS%20Oka%20asked.%20Mr%20Balaji's%20counsel%20sought%20time%20to%20return%20with%20instructions%20and%20the%20matter%20was%20posted%20for%20December%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...the%20current%20application%20is%20based%20on%20the%20apprehension%20that%20immediately%20after%20we%20enlarged%20the%20respondent%20no.%202%20(Balaji)%20on%20bail%20by%20order%20dated%2026%20September%2C%202024%20the%20second%20respondent%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20a%20Cabinet%20Minister...%20the%20apprehension%20is%20that%20considering%20the%20seriousness%20of%20allegations%20against%20the%20second%20respondent%20in%20the%20predicate%20offences%2C%20the%20witnesses%20may%20not%20be%20in%20the%20frame%20of%20mind%20to%20depose%20against%20the%20second%20respondent%20who%20is%20holding%20the%20position%20of%20cabinet%20minister...%20This%20is%20the%20only%20aspect%20on%20which%20prima%20facie%20we%20are%20inclined%20to%20consider%20the%20application%2C%20and%20while%20making%20it%20clear%20that%20there%20is%20no%20reason%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20judgment%20on%20merits%20and%20adjudication%20of%20the%20application%20remains%20confined%20to%20the%20aforesaid%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForty-nine-year-old%20Senthil%20Balaji%20is%20a%20four-term%20MLA%20who%20started%20his%20political%20career%20with%20the%20DMK%2C%20then%20switched%20to%20the%20AIADMK%20before%20returning%20to%20the%20DMK.%20He%20was%20arrested%20in%20June%20last%20year%20in%20connection%20with%20corruption%20allegations%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20Tamil%20Nadu%20transport%20minister%20in%20the%20J%20Jayalalithaa%20government%20from%202011%20to%202015.%20Eight%20months%20after%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20arrested%20him%2C%20he%20resigned%20as%20minister.%20Days%20after%20he%20was%20released%20on%20bail%20in%20September%2C%20the%20MK%20Stalin%20government%20reinstated%20him%20as%20minister%20with%20key%20portfolios%20of%20electricity%2C%20excise%20and%20prohibition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWelcomi