%20to%20avoid%20falling%20victim%20to%20such%20scams.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bangladesh%20Estimates%20%2416%20Billion%20Siphoned%20Yearly%20During%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20Rule%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20average%20%2416%20billion%20may%20have%20been%20illicitly%20siphoned%20out%20of%20Bangladesh%20annually%20during%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%2015-year%20rule%2C%20according%20to%20the%20findings%20of%20a%20committee%20formed%20by%20interim%20leader%20Muhammad%20Yunus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20led%20by%20economist%20Debapriya%20Bhattacharya%20submitted%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20the%20state%20of%20Bangladesh's%20economy%20to%20Yunus%20in%20Dhaka%20on%20Sunday%2C%20according%20to%20a%20government%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20was%20ousted%20by%20student%20protesters%20in%20August%20after%2015%20years%20of%20increasingly%20authoritarian%20rule.%20The%20army%20and%20protest%20leaders%20tapped%20Nobel%20laureate%20Yunus%2C%20who%20pioneered%20microcredit%20to%20the%20poor%2C%20to%20lead%20an%20interim%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20blood%20curdles%20to%20know%20how%20they%20plundered%20the%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Yunus%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%20%26quot%3BThe%20sad%20part%20is%20they%20looted%20the%20economy%20openly.%20And%20most%20of%20us%20could%20not%20summon%20courage%20to%20confront%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20shows%20%26quot%3Bthe%20economy%20we%20inherited%20after%20the%20July-August%20mass%20uprising%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20in%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20party%20are%20in%20jail%20or%20hiding%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20or%20have%20left%20the%20country.%20The%20party%20doesn't%20have%20a%20spokesperson%20who%20can%20be%20contacted%20to%20comment%20on%20allegations%20in%20the%20white%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20investigations%2C%20the%20committee%20looked%20into%20seven%20large%20projects%20out%20of%2029%20which%20had%20more%20than%20100%20billion%20taka%20(%24836%20million)%20expenditure%20outlay%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20cost%20of%20the%20seven%20projects%20examined%20was%20estimated%20at%201.14%20trillion%20taka.%20Hasina's%20government%20later%20revised%20project%20costs%20to%201.95%20trillion%20taka%20through%20the%20addition%20of%20more%20components%20and%20inflated%20land%20prices%20among%20others%2C%20according%20to%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20is%20deeper%20than%20what%20we%20have%20thought%2C%26quot%3B%20Bhattacharya%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20400-page%20white%20paper%20will%20show%20%26quot%3Bhow%20crony%20capitalism%20gave%20birth%20to%20the%20oligarchs%2C%20who%20controlled%20the%20policy%20framing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733123580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fpp02ivl_sheikh-hasina-ians_625x300_28_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbangladesh-estimates-16-billion-siphoned-yearly-in-sheikh-hasina-rule-7153013%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20average%20%2416%20billion%20may%20have%20been%20illicitly%20siphoned%20out%20of%20Bangladesh%20annually%20during%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%2015-year%20rule.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbangladesh-estimates-16-billion-siphoned-yearly-in-sheikh-hasina-rule-7153013%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'We%20grant%20bail%2C%20you%20become%20minister%20next%20day!'%3A%20SC%20in%20Senthil%20Balaji%20case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733123509000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115891449%2Cimgsize-941616.cms%22%2C%22originID%