his%20party%20and%20Congress%2C%20or%20any%20INDIA%20bloc%20partner%2C%20for%20the%20Delhi%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-attacked-what-was-my-fault-arvind-kejriwal-after-liquid-attack-at-aap-rally-7146298%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20no%20alliance%20in%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20fought%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Elections%20together%2C%20but%20it%20ended%20in%20a%20debacle%20as%20the%20BJP%20won%20all%20seats.%20The%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20were%20also%20engaged%20in%20seat-sharing%20talks%20before%20the%20Haryana%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20October%2C%20but%20the%20talks%20failed%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20won%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP-Congress%20break-up%20has%20been%20mocked%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20AAP's%20clearest%20rival%20in%20the%20February%20election.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20coming%20together%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election...%20they%20lacked%20ambition%20and%20could%20not%20win%20any%20seat%20in%20Delhi.%20Now%2C%20this%20is%20the%20'friendship%20with%20benefits'%20model.%20Here%20they%20are%20saying%20they%20will%20contest%20against%20each%20other%20but%20come%20together%20in%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20Shehzad%20Ponnawalla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20newest%20recruit%20-%20former%20AAP%20leader%20Kailash%20Gahlot%20-%20also%20threw%20in%20a%20jab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20people%20of%20Delhi%20have%20decided%20to%20bring%20the%20BJP%20to%20power.%20In%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20there%20was%20no%20impact%20of%20alliance%20(between%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress).%20People%20of%20Delhi%20are%20troubled%20due%20to%20damaged%20roads%2C%20overflowing%20sewers%20and%20other%20issues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20will%20person