their%20religious%20sites%2C%20what%20will%20happen%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight-wing%20outfit%20Hindu%20Sena%20has%20filed%20the%20petition%20linked%20to%20the%20dargah.%20While%20admitting%20it%2C%20the%20Ajmer%20court%20has%20sought%20responses%20from%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI)%2C%20the%20Dargah%20committee%20and%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Minority%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20will%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20respond%2C%20they%20send%20chadars%20too.%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20sent%2010%20chadars%20in%2010%20years.%20How%20will%20he%20respond%3F%20BJP-RSS%20must%20stop%20this.%20This%20is%20not%20in%20the%20country's%20response%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20witty%20wordplay%2C%20the%20AIMIM%20leader%20said%20we%20should%20now%20forget%20about%20AI%20and%20talk%20only%20about%20ASI.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20talk%20about%20artificial%20intelligence%3B%20just%20keep%20doing%20ASI%2C%20ASI%2C%20and%20just%20keep%20digging.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20structures%20hundreds%20of%20years%20old%20can%20also%20be%20found%20under%20the%20house%20of%20a%20BJP%20leader%20in%20Delhi.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20how%20a%20civilisation%20progresses%2C%20this%20is%20weakening%20India.%20There%20are%20other%20issues%2C%20unemployment%2C%20price%20rise%2C%20farmer%20deaths%20and%20China%20getting%20stronger.%20But%20you%20are%20stuck%20with%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Owaisi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AIMIM%20leader%20said%20that%20he%20had%20warned%20after%20the%20Babri%20Masjid-Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20judgment%20that%20such%20issues%20would%20crop%20up.%20%26quot%3BIf%20DY%20Chandrachud%20stopped%20this%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20the%20end%20of%20the%20chapter.%20He%20made%20wrong%20oral%20observations.%20So%20at%2015%20places%2C%20such%20attempts%20are%20being%20made%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AIMIM%20leader%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India's%20observations%20during%20a%20hearing%20on%20the%20Gyanvapi%20case.%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20then%20said%20that%20the%201991%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%20does%20not%20bar%20ascertaining%20the%20religious%20character%20of%20a%20place.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Act%20says%20you%20can't%20alter%20or%20convert%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20place.%20They're%20not%20seeking%20conversion%20of%20the%20place.%20The%20question%20is%20what%20is%20the%20status%20of%20the%20place%20as%20of%20August%2015%2C%201947.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201991%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%20prohibits%20the%20conversion%20of%20any%20place%20of%20worship%20and%20provides%20for%20the%20maintenance%20of%20the%20religious%20character%20of%20any%20place%20of%20worship%20as%20it%20existed%20on%20August%2015%2C%201947.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20say%20what%20is%20the%20problem%20with%20ascertaining.%20Is%20this%20an%20academic%20exercise%3F%20You%20want%20to%20change%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Owaisi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733118360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fnooo89sg_owaisi-dyc-_625x300_02_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fasaduddin-owaisi-ajmer-sharif-forget-ai-talk-only-asi-keep-digging-a-owaisi-amid-ajmer-sharif-row-7152256%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20row%20over%20a%20Rajasthan%20court%20admitting%20a%20petition%20that%20claims%20that%20the%20Ajmer%20Sharif%20dargah%20was%20built%20over%20a%20Shiva%20temple%2C%20AIMIM%20leader%20and%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20has%20said%20the%20dargah%20goes%20back%20800%20years%20and%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWhere%20will%20this%20stop%3F%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fasaduddin-owaisi-ajmer-sharif-forget-ai-talk-only-asi-keep-digging-a-owaisi-amid-ajmer-sharif-row-7152256%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2