cally%20drag%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20alliance%20into%20war%20with%20Moscow%20if%20Ukraine%20joins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Kyiv%2C%20Zelenskyy%20said%20that%20any%20invitation%20for%20Ukraine%20to%20join%20NATO%20still%20has%20to%20recognize%20all%20of%20its%20territory%20as%20Ukrainian%2C%20including%20areas%20occupied%20by%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20his%20reason%20was%20that%20NATO%2Fthe%20alliance%20couldn't%20extend%20an%20invitation%20to%20only%20a%20%26quot%3Bpart%20of%20the%20territory%20of%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eurointegration.com.ua%2Fnews%2F2024%2F12%2F1%2F7199639%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20Ukrainian%20media.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelenskyy%20added%20that%20Ukraine%20%26quot%3Bwould%20never%20accept%26quot%3B%20an%20accession%20plan%20that%20says%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20we%20understand%20that%20Article%205%2C%20when%20you're%20a%20member%20of%20NATO%2C%20cannot%20apply%20to%20the%20entire%20territory%20of%20Ukraine%20during%20wartime%2C%20as%20countries%20are%20against%20the%20risks%20of%20being%20drawn%20into%20the%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20proposal%20could%20essentially%20split%20Ukraine%20into%20two%20regions%20as%20far%20as%20NATO%20is%20concerned.%20The%20region%20that%20includes%20all%20of%20Ukraine's%20current%20territory%2C%20like%20Kyiv%20and%20Kharkiv%2C%20would%20have%20to%20be%20defended.%20There%20would%20be%20no%20obligation%20for%20the%20rest%2C%20which%20is%20the%20Ukrainian%20territory%20seized%20by%20Russia%20in%20the%20east.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20launched%20a%20campaign%20this%20week%20to%20pressure%20NATO%20into%20extending%20an%20invitation%20to%20Kyiv%2C%20a%20move%20the%20alliance%20already%20promised%20in%202008%20would%20eventually%20happen.%20NATO%20has%20not%20provided%20a%20specific%20timeline%20for%20when%20that%20invitation%20might%2