wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EParikshit%E2%80%99s%20model%20of%20Cow%20Currency%20has%20been%20welcomed%20by%20many%20customers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJyoti%E2%80%99s%20husband%20is%20my%20friend%20and%20when%20I%20got%20to%20know%20she%20had%20established%20a%20dairy%20farm%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20use%20of%20the%20opportunity.%20When%20Jyoti%20was%20interested%20as%20well%2C%20I%20was%20happy%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Parikshit.%20After%20contemplating%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20the%20duo%20decided%20to%20get%20involved%20with%20Cow%20Currency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20personally%20believe%20a%20woman%20can%20provide%20the%20right%20guidance%20for%20a%20business%20venture.%20Women%20are%20Lakshmi%20for%20me.%20And%20for%20Cow%20Currency%2C%20it%20is%20Jyoti%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%201%2C08%2C000%2C%20customers%20own%20a%20cow%20for%20three%20years.%20The%20farm%20takes%20full%20responsibility%20for%20the%20cow%E2%80%99s%20maintenance%2C%20feeding%2C%20and%20healthcare.%20In%20return%2C%20customers%20receive%20two%20litres%20of%20fresh%20A2%20milk%20daily%20and%20two%20kilograms%20of%20%3Cem%3Eghee%3C%2Fem%3E%20every%20month%2C%20delivered%20to%20their%20homes.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20a%20customer%20is%20in%20a%20different%20state%2C%20we%20courier%20the%20%3Cem%3Eghee%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20the%20milk%20expense%20is%20credited%20to%20their%20account%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Jyoti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20a%20cow%E2%80%99s%20natural%20four-month%20dry%20period%20each%20year%2C%20Cow%20Currency%20guarantees%20an%20uninterrupted%20milk%20supply%20by%20pooling%20resources%20from%20multiple%20cows.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20makes%20the%20model%20affordable%2C%20with%20milk%20costing%20just%20Rs%2045%20per%20litre%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Parikshit.%20After%20three%20years%2C%20customers%20also%20receive%20Rs%2022%2C000%20as%20an%20end-of-term%20payout%2C%20encouraging%20long-term%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20customers%20are%20provided%20with%20a%20proper%20breed%20certificate%20of%20the%20cow%20and%20its%20genetic%20parents%20to%20ensure%20the%20purity%20of%20the%20breed.%20In%20fact%2C%20customers%20are%20welcome%20to%20meet%20their%20pet%20cow%20whenever%20they%20wish.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20able%20to%20play%20with%20%3Cem%3ERadha%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20farm%2C%20and%20the%20feeling%20of%20owning%20a%20cow%20is%20something%20unexplainable%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Simple%20H%20Singh%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFulfilling%20urban%20needs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20customers%20like%20Puspanjali%20Dutta%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Cow%20Currency%E2%80%99%20model%20rekindles%20childhood%20memories.%20%E2%80%9CI%20missed%20drinking%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Fis-your-milk-adulterated-shorts-food-foodsafety%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epure%20cow%E2%80%99s%20milk%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20moving%20to%20the%20city%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20I%20have%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20drinking%20milk%20from%20my%20own%20cow%2C%20which%20I%E2%80%99ve%20named%20Rivan.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20in%20urban%20cities%20do%20not%20have%20the%20time%20or%20space%20to%20care%20for%20the%20cow.%20This%20model%20fulfils%20that%20in%20the%20best%20way%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20Puspanjali%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimple%2C%20who%20has%20Celiac%20disease%2C%20highlights%20the%20product%E2%80%99s%20health%20benefits.%20%E2%80%9CPackaged%20milk%20always%20causes%20allergic%20reactions%20for%20me.%20But%20for%20the%20past%20six%20months%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20had%20no%20issues%20with%20their%20milk%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20620px)%20100vw%2C%20620px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-11_11zon-1732802283.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22620%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Graphic%20explanation%20of%20Cow%20Currency%20and%20its%20benefits.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-11_11zon-1732802283.jpg%20620w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-11_11zon-1732802283-294x300.jpg%20294w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-11_11zon-1732802283-500x510.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-11_11zon-1732802283-150x153.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-384022%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22632%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGraphic%20explanation%20of%20Cow%20Currency%20and%20its%20benefits.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EEthical%20treatment%20of%20cows%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20Cow%20Currency%E2%80%99s%20philosophy.%20%E2%80%9CCows%20are%20often%20abandoned%20or%20sent%20to%20slaughterhouses%20when%20they%20stop%20producing%20milk.%20We%20ensure%20every%20cow%20has%20a%20safe%20and%20respectful%20life%20beyond%20its%20milking%20period%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parikshit%2C%20who%20has%20over%2018%20years%20of%20farming%20experience%2C%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20pilot%20phase%2C%20Cow%20Currency%20operates%20with%2025%20staff%20members%20per%20farm%20and%20already%20serves%20over%2070%20satisfied%20customers.%20The%20duo%20plans%20to%20expand%20to%2075%20farms%20across%20India%2C%20enabling%20more%20people%20to%20reconnect%20with%20ethical%2C%20high-quality%20dairy%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJyoti%E2%80%99s%20journey%20from%20a%20concerned%20mother%20to%20a%20successful%20entrepreneur%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20her%20unwavering%20dedication%20to%20quality%20and%20sustainability.%20Her%20ventures%20not%20only%20meet%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20pure%20dairy%20products%20but%20also%20champion%20ethical%20farming%20practices.%20As%20she%20proudly%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20strive%20to%20ensure%20our%20cows%20are%20happy%20and%20healthy%2C%20and%20our%20customers%20feel%20connected%20to%20the%20source%20of%20their%20food.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CReal%20wealth%20is%20owning%20a%20cow%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parikshit%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Jyoti%20and%20Parikshit%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jerseygirlorganics.co.nz%2Fpost%2Fcan-you-drink-a2-milk-if-you-are-lactose-intolerant%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECan%20you%20drink%20A2%20milk%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20lactose%20intolerant%3F%E2%80%99%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Jersey%20Girl%20Organics%2C%20Published%20on%208%20November%2C%202021%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fnutrition%2Fa1-vs-a2-milk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA1%20vs.%20A2%20Milk%20%E2%80%94%20Does%20It%20Matter%3F%E2%80%99%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Healthline%2C%20Published%20on%2017%20July%2C%202023%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbadgut.org%2Finfo