0on%20species%20like%20%3Cem%3Eber%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20Jujube)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekhejri%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejaal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Pilu%20Tree)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekumatiya%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Acacia%20Senegal)%2C%20which%20are%20native%20to%20the%20region.%20%E2%80%9CChinkaras%20and%20blackbucks%20love%20%3Cem%3Eber%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20lot%2C%20so%20we%20plant%20those%20every%20year%20to%20replant%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F60652%2Ffighting-deforestation-oran-rajasthan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20lands%20of%20Oran%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrans%20%E2%80%94%20sacred%20groves%20that%20have%20traditionally%20been%20protected%20by%20rural%20communities%20%E2%80%94%20play%20a%20central%20role%20in%20Sharvan%E2%80%99s%20conservation%20efforts.%20These%20groves%20are%20rich%20in%20biodiversity%20and%20often%20include%20water%20bodies%20that%20are%20crucial%20for%20the%20survival%20of%20local%20wildlife.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Sharvan%E2%80%99s%20significant%20breakthroughs%20came%20when%20he%20and%20his%20team%20began%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20water%20ponds.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ponds%20that%20were%20supposed%20to%20be%20for%20the%20animals%20to%20drink%20from%20were%20being%20dug%20too%20deep%20for%20them%20to%20reach%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20This%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20smaller%20animals%2C%20like%20rabbits%2C%20to%20access%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20inspiration%20from%20the%20shallow%20saucer-like%20ponds%20he%20had%20seen%20at%20Tal%20Chhapar%20Sanctuary%20in%20Nagaur%2C%20Sharvan%20and%20his%20team%2C%20with%20funding%20from%20Intact%20(Chapter%20Jodhpur)%20built%20shallow%20water%20ponds%20in%20the%20Orans%2C%20making%20them%20accessible%20to%20a%20wider%20variety%20of%20wildlife.%20The%20results%20were%20immediate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20we%20made%20a%20video%20about%20how%20we%20had%20built%20these%20ponds%2C%2030%20people%20called%20us%20from%20other%20areas%2C%20including%20Nagaur%2C%20Bikaner%2C%20and%20Barmer%2C%20to%20ask%20if%20we%20could%20help%20them%20do%20the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharvan%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202407px)%20100vw%2C%202407px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-2.30.09-PM-1_11zon-1732714129.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222407%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Watering%20hole%20inspired%20by%20Tal%20Chhapar%20Sanctuary%2C%20Nagaur%20being%20filled%20with%20water%20for%20every%20animal%2C%20from%20rabbits%20to%20birds%20and%20deer.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-2.30.09-PM-1_11zon-1732714129.jpeg%202407w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-2.30.09-PM-1_11zon-1732714129-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-2.30.09-PM-1_11zon-1732714129-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-2.30.09-PM-1_11zon-1732714129-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-2.30.09-PM-1_11zon-1732714129-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-2.30.09-PM-1_11zon-1732714129-2048x1536.jpeg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-2.30.09-PM-1_11zon-17