aption%5C%22%3ERecording%20the%20song%20that%20would%20receive%20a%20Grammy%20nomination.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20a%20long%20and%20detailed%20discussion%20about%20what%20he%20wanted%20from%20me%20over%20a%20call%20and%20I%20recorded%20my%20part%20in%20Bengaluru.%20The%20recording%20I%20received%20already%20had%20Anushka%E2%80%99s%20wonderful%20sitar%20parts%20recorded%20and%20it%20sounded%20wonderful.%20But%20I%20had%20an%20incredible%20time%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20blend%20into%20this%20mix%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98voicetrumentalist%E2%80%99%20(where%20there%20are%20no%20lyrics%20but%20I%20still%20sing%20and%20use%20various%20improvisational%20styles).%20So%2C%20I%20had%20to%20weave%20in%2C%20find%20my%20own%20space%20on%20the%20record%20and%20add%20something%20of%20value%20to%20it.%20My%20objective%20was%20not%20to%20hamper%20the%20intention%20of%20the%20composition%20but%20add%20to%20the%20already%20existing%20soul%20of%20the%20song%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EVARI%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20has%20been%20filled%20with%20notable%20events%20for%20Varijashree.%20In%20addition%20to%20her%20Grammy%20nomination%2C%20she%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20artist%20to%20perform%20at%20the%20esteemed%20Jazz%20al%20Parque%20Festival%20in%20Bogot%C3%A1%2C%20Colombia%2C%20in%20October.%20Following%20this%20performance%2C%20she%20showcased%20her%20vocal%20prowess%20as%20the%20featured%20soloist%20in%20%E2%80%98Mahabharata%20%E2%80%93%20Mantras%2C%20Fights%2C%20and%20Threnody%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20opera%20by%20Riccardo%20Nova%2C%20performed%20with%20the%20Ensemble%20MusikFabrik%20in%20Florence%2C%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20she%20released%20her%20eponymous%20original%20album%20%E2%80%98VARI%E2%80%99.%20The%20album%20was%20produced%20by%20Grammy%20Award-winning%20artist%20Michael%20League%20of%20Snarky%20Puppy%20and%20features%20