with%20governance%20and%20the%20world.%20Through%20captivating%20videos%2C%20films%2C%20and%20documentaries%2C%20they%20are%20creating%20a%20hyperlocal%20communication%20network%20that%20empowers%20tribes%20to%20address%20everyday%20challenges%20and%20engage%20with%20the%20Government%20like%20never%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20all%20began%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20Aadiwasi%20Janjagruti%20traces%20back%20to%202016%2C%20when%20Nitesh%20Bhardwaj%20(33)%2C%20one%20of%20its%20founders%2C%20arrived%20in%20Dhadgaon%20for%20a%20fellowship%20programme.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Nitesh%20was%20passionate%20about%20filmmaking%20but%20had%20no%20plans%20for%20long-term%20involvement%20in%20the%20village.%20His%20connection%20with%20the%20community%20began%20unexpectedly%20%E2%80%94%20through%20a%20group%20of%20eager%20high%20school%20students%20curious%20about%20video%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20equipment%20or%20resources%2C%20Nitesh%20started%20teaching%20the%20students%20how%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333099%2Fwomentaries-women-changemaker-stories-film-documentaries-winners-awards%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshoot%20and%20edit%20videos%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20just%20his%20and%20a%20friend%E2%80%99s%20phones.%20Their%20first%20project%20was%20a%20simple%2C%20zero-budget%20video%2C%20but%20its%20impact%20was%20profound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20uploaded%20