Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Preeti%20had%20her%20daughters%20and%20saw%20them%20struggle%20in%20their%20schools%2C%20she%20realised%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20problem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20daughters%20go%20to%20a%20much%20better%20school%20than%20I%20did.%20So%2C%20when%20they%20got%20their%20period%2C%20the%20problem%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20water%20or%20cleanliness.%20It%20was%20that%20they%20still%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20like%20the%20environment%20was%20safe%20enough%20to%20speak%20about%20it%20openly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Preeti%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGetting%20rid%20of%20taboos%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202018%2C%20Prazna%20Foundation%20was%20established%20to%20ensure%20that%20girls%20in%20underprivileged%20areas%20would%20not%20face%20the%20same%20challenges%20Preeti%20faced.%20The%20organisation%20began%20as%20a%20response%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20menstrual%20hygiene%20education%2C%20access%20to%20sanitary%20products%2C%20and%20the%20silence%20surrounding%20menstruation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20menstrual%20health%20education%20a%20universal%20right%20and%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20barriers%20that%20prevent%20underprivileged%20children%20and%20women%20from%20getting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F369350%2Fdr-abhay-bang-rani-search-gadchiroli-maharashtra-tribal-healthcare-access%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproper%20education%20and%20healthcare%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Preeti.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20achieve%20that%20goal%2C%20Prazna%20launched%20Project%20Kishori%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20educate%20young%20girls%20about%20menstrual%20hygiene%20and%20provide%20them%20with%20essential%20hygiene%20kits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Preeti%20speaking%20to%20a%20group%20of%20girls%20at%20a%20government%20school%20in%20Jaipur%2C%20educating%20them%20about%20menstrual%20health%2C%20the%20importance%20of%20hygiene%2C%20and%20empowering%20them%20to%20speak%20openly%20about%20periods%20without%20shame.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305-1200x900.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305-800x600.jpeg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305-600x450.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305-400x300.jpeg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_