each%2C%20Prazna%20has%20already%20educated%20over%2020%2C000%20women%20on%20menstruation%20and%20hygiene.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20unique%20about%20Project%20Kishori%20is%20its%20approach%20to%20breaking%20down%20the%20taboos%20around%20menstruation%20through%20peer-to-peer%20interaction.%20In%20each%20school%2C%20%E2%80%98Kishori%20Clubs%E2%80%99%20were%20established%2C%20bringing%20together%20girls%20who%20would%20lead%20conversations%20and%20share%20their%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20seen%20a%20lot%20of%20girls%2C%20especially%20if%20they%20get%20their%20periods%20young%2C%20get%20very%20nervous.%20They%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20it.%20What%20Prazna%20and%20Preeti%20do%20is%20give%20a%20certain%20sense%20of%20reassurance%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%C2%A0%20Kavita%20Sharma%2C%20principal%20of%20a%20government%20school%20in%20Jaipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20also%20help%20girls%20navigate%20this%20next%20stage%20of%20their%20life%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20emotionally%2C%20mentally%20or%20physically%2C%20because%20it%20is%20a%20lot%20for%20one%20small%20person%20to%20go%20through%20on%20their%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20trust%20and%20understanding%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20creating%20an%20environment%20where%20girls%20feel%20comfortable%2C%20the%20programme%20encourages%20ongoing%20conversations%20about%20menstrual%20health.%20One%20strategy%20employed%20by%20Prazna%20was%20to%20use%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F278313%2Fsundarbans-hingalganj-island-english-medium-school-inspiring-teacher-kolkata%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efemale%20teachers%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20intermediaries%20%E2%80%94%20trusted%20adults%20who%20could%20help%20faci