20many%20young%20girls%20have%20anaemia%20and%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20constantly%20take%20supplements%20for%20that.%20They%20need%20to%20be%20educated%20about%20good%20food%20as%20well%2C%20and%20when%20the%20situation%20is%20bad%20we%20do%20involve%20and%20educate%20the%20parents%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20Preeti%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20help%20people%20understand%20technical%20know-hows.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20helping%20with%20workshops%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20foundation%2C%20so%20I%20know%20what%20kind%20of%20questions%20people%20have%20regarding%20menses%20and%20the%20myths%20attached%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Shailja%20Jain%2C%20a%20gynaecologist%20and%20close%20associate%20of%20Preeti.%20She%20trains%20the%20volunteers%20so%20that%20they%20are%20properly%20prepared%20when%20speaking%20to%20inquisitive%20young%20girls%20who%20might%20have%20some%20interesting%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20also%20works%20closely%20with%20Deepika%20Godara%2C%20an%20advocate%20who%20engages%20with%20slum%20dwelling%20women%20and%20gives%20them%20a%20run%20down%20of%20their%20basic%20human%20rights.%20%E2%80%9CSure%20our%20country%20got%20independence%20in%201947%2C%20but%20the%20women%20are%20still%20not%20free.%20There%E2%80%99s%20domestic%20abuse%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358515%2Fwheat-stalk-painting-from-bahraich-uttar-pradesh-girls-training-early-marriage-entrepreneurship%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ea%20lack%20of%20proper%20healthcare%2C%20and%20so%20much%20misinformation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.02.20-PM-1-1732171813-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20wid