oes%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20informing%20women%20about%20helpline%20numbers%2C%20government%20policies%2C%20and%20other%20resources%20they%20have%20at%20their%20disposal%2C%20she%20gives%20them%20the%20power%20to%20take%20charge%20of%20their%20own%20lives.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20complaints%20of%20domestic%20abuse%20filed%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F369350%2Fdr-abhay-bang-rani-search-gadchiroli-maharashtra-tribal-healthcare-access%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslum%20or%20labour%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20not%20taken%20seriously.%20So%2C%20we%20ask%20the%20women%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20when%20their%20complaint%20is%20being%20written%20down%2C%20it%20should%20be%20written%20on%20a%20paper%20of%20a%20particular%20colour%2C%20so%20they%20know%20it%E2%80%99s%20actually%20being%20filed%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Deepika.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20men%20a%20part%20of%20the%20conversation%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20inspiring%20aspects%20of%20Prazna%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20the%20way%20they%E2%80%99ve%20involved%20male%20teachers%20and%20male%20students%20in%20the%20conversation.%20Historically%2C%20menstruation%20has%20been%20seen%20as%20a%20topic%20for%20women%20only%20which%20makes%20it%20an%20isolating%20%E2%80%98us%20and%20them%E2%80%99%20experience.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20gone%20to%20a%20government%20school%2C%20and%20a%20teacher%20asked%20us%20to%20include%20the%20boys%20of%20the%20class%20in%20the%20workshop%20as%20well.%20And%20we%20were%20more%20than%20happy%20to%20include%20this%20idea%20in%20our%20manner%20of%20working%2C%E2%80%9D%20Preeti%20notes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMale%20teachers%20and%20volunteers%20have%20also%20been%20involved%20in%20workshops%2C%20breaking%20down%20barriers%20of%20shame%20and%20making%20the%20topic%20more%20inclusive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20have%20been%20encouraging.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20kind%20of%20knew%20what%20menstruation%20was.%20But%20earlier%2C%20I%20used%20to%20feel%20hesitant%20to%20speak%20about%20these%20things%2C%20especially%20at%20home.%20I%20used%20to%20feel%20that%20maybe%20this%20is%20something%20that%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20kept%20a%20secret.%20But%20then%20when%20we%20saw%20our%20teachers%2C%20and%20people%20from%20Prazna%2C%20speak%20about%20these%20things%2C%20that%20hesitancy%20has%20gone%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sonali%2C%20a%20Class%2010%20student%20from%20Jaipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20its%20grassroots%20work%2C%20Prazna%20also%20advocates%20for%20comprehensive%20national%20policies.%20While%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20programmes%20which%20distribute%20pads%2C%20Preeti%20believes%20that%20menstrual%20education%20needs%20to%20go%20beyond%20just%20providing%20products.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20good%20to%20give%20pads%2C%20but%20there%20should%20be%20a%20programme%20that%20happens%20at%20least%20every%20few%20weeks%20where%20the%20conversation%20is%20reopened%20and%20there%20is%20a%20continuous%20dialogue.%20Because%20a%20taboo%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20eased%20with%20a%20single%20workshop%2C%E2%80%9D%20Preeti%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%2C%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Preeti%20Sharma%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732512431000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D381663%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prazna%20Foundation's%20Project%20Kishori%20is%20breaking%20the%20silence%20around%20menstruation%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20creating%20safe%20spaces%20for%20young%20girls%20to%20learn%20about%20their%20bodies%2C%20and%20talk%20openly%20about%20their%20menstrual%20health.%22%2C%22aut